        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="pTHoVpohA2qwFMVxUgUg-51" value="5.如果 leaderCommit &amp;gt; commitIndex，则将commitIndex更新为 min(leaderCommit, 最后一个新条目的索引)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1" vertex="1">
